{
  "text": "The packed bed adsorption has a number of advantages: it is simple to operate, attains a high yield and it can be easily scaled up from a laboratory-scale procedure. The stages in the separation protocol can also be automated and high degrees of purification can often be achieved in a single step process [CITATION_1] .",
